.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/_techspec_soul.md:524:Future extension points may add typed persona overlays or resource-backed soul catalogs only after a separate TechSpec defines precedence, audit trails, conflict handling, and agent-operable rollback. Such future work must remain additive to the authoritative `SOUL.md` snapshot model and must not turn hooks or capabilities into prompt mutation backdoors.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/_techspec_soul.md:530:- `agh agent soul validate <agent>` validates frontmatter, reserved sections, size limits, and forbidden operational declarations.
