.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/_techspec_soul.md:532:- `agh agent soul write <agent> --file <path>|--stdin --expected-digest <digest> --json` validates and atomically writes `SOUL.md`.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/_techspec_soul.md:533:- `agh agent soul delete <agent> --expected-digest <digest> --json` removes `SOUL.md` through the managed authoring service.
