.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/_techspec_soul.md:573:Spawned sessions do not inherit the parent session's `SOUL.md`. A spawned session resolves the target agent's own `SOUL.md`, then applies explicit spawn fields already present in `internal/api/contract/agents.go` (`AgentSpawnRequest.SpawnRole`, `AgentSpawnRequest.PromptOverlay`) and `internal/session/spawn.go` (`SpawnOpts.SpawnRole`, `SpawnOpts.PromptOverlay`).
