.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-010.md:13:AGH features are incomplete if they are only internal Go calls or web UI controls. Agent Soul already chose managed authoring with CLI, HTTP, UDS, and Host API parity. `HEARTBEAT.md` depends on session health to be useful, so both the artifact and runtime health state need agent-operable surfaces.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-010.md:17:MVP manageability covers both `HEARTBEAT.md` policy and session health:
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-010.md:19:- `agent heartbeat` surfaces manage the authored artifact and resolved policy.
