.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-010.md:25:There is no explicit heartbeat refresh surface in MVP. Policy writes create new snapshots, and wake decisions evaluate the latest valid snapshot at wake-decision time. The snapshot id and digest used for a wake are recorded on the wake event and synthetic prompt metadata.
