.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-006.md:47:- **Cons**: Leaves `SOUL.md` authoring as out-of-band filesystem work and weakens agent manageability.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-006.md:52:- **Description**: CLI, HTTP, UDS, Host API, and web each write `SOUL.md` with local validation.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-006.md:62:- **Why rejected**: Overlay systems are future work. V1 must first establish the canonical managed authoring path for `SOUL.md`.
.compozy/tasks/agent-soul/adrs/adr-006.md:88:- Treat `expected_digest` as mandatory when replacing or deleting an existing `SOUL.md`.
